Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to explore\Nthe Sunken Ruins of Melusine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we decided to leave Erisen for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunken Ruins of Melusine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be\Naround here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature looks the same everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like the sunset\NI saw by the ocean in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like such a long time ago,\Nthough it hasn't even been six months yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our time here has been too hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:03:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the proof of\Nconquest from Gruen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's glowing with light!\NThat's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a bit mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty presentation, unlike\Nthe tastes of some other Liberator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. This feels like actual fantasy;\NI'm actually a bit moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, no wonder why I couldn't\Nfind it when searching normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was dumb of me to hope\NI'd just stumble upon the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flow is quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another turbulent boat ride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's approaching from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has black-red magic power;\Nit must be a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good moment to test my new weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, looks like I was able\Nto make it more powerful. Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fifth one. Five pentagram\Nsymbols and five locations,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this pendant\Nwith some light left in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to this place using just magic\Nwould have been very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would have had to notice this pattern\Nright away or run out of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really have to thank Master's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the real starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels more like just a cave,\Nnot a "Sunken Ruin", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it wasn't entirely underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Yue handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh... Um, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's\Nsomething on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime... This is a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is getting gradually deeper.\NThis is good for you too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're looking quite cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the position most\Nrecently occupied by Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So, should I call you\NYue-{\i1}chan {\i0}from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perish, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so violent to only me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Don't you think they're too weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for monsters in a Great Labyrinth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, I got burned.\NCan you rub some medicine on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously trying\Nto do this right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-{\i1}san {\i0}and Tio-{\i1}san {\i0}seem to be on a\Nrampage, I thought we had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring cleansing and healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... There goes my shot at\Ngetting him to touch my breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime, it looks like\Nthis jelly melts magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I was wondering why\Nmy flames lost power so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even the magic\Npowering the flames are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is finally starting\Nto feel like a Great Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, go on the offensive!\NI'll handle defense! Herem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? I'm getting monster\Nreadings from the entire room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what a\NGreat Labyrinth monster is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, we can't let\Nit regenerate forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is its mana crystal core?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've mentioned it,\Nit's transparent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't see a mana crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing has no mana crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No mana crystal? Are you saying\Nit's not actually a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm seeing through my Demon Eye\Nis that it's black-red colored overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if the whole jelly-like body\Nis one big mana crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole body?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole room is the same color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're already trapped in its belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's regain our footing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an open space\Nunderneath the ground here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it leads!\NBrace yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I guess... Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all carrying smaller versions\Nof the Treasure Trove.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be able\Nto manage on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking\Nabout all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me, and not Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought you'd die on your own,\Nbut Yue can take care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I could tell from her look\Nthat she wanted me to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. We're partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop wasting time being depressed,\Nwe need to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in a Great Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just spaced out for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just keep exploring until\Nwe reach the bottom. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue and the others are\Nprobably doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship graveyard or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all look like warships.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the biggest ship seems different.\NDoesn't it look like a passenger ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I in a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll block this! Holy Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this isn't just a normal illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not entirely real either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physical attacks have no effect,\Nbut attacks including magic power work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the effect is the same\Nas long as magic power is involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter the effect or attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Did I just kill that person...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't real. Just think of it as\Nan illusion that you can manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I was confused\Nfor a moment, but I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our god!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hail Ehit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heathens! Die before the glory of our god!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori! We're jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do we get out\Nof this creepy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's an exit?\NMaybe one of the ships is an exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are hundreds of ships;\Nwe can't search every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war would end by\Nthe time we're done searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Maybe we can end the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End? Oh, you mean,\Nkill them all, for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that idea. Let's go, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's related\Nto these derelict ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a recreation of a war that\Ntook place in the past, using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the added twist of attacking\Nthe explorer of the Great Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be the concept\Nof this particular Great Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each Great Labyrinth has\Na concept, set by a Liberator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then this one would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show the tragedy of what\Nthe crazed god can bring about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I know how it feels\Nto get almost swallowed by insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost went insane\Nat the bottom of the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't, thanks to... Yue?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what would have\Nhappened to me if I didn't meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was the one to hold\Nyou together and protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I don't know what\NI would have been able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even keep a single promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy. Yue is quite a tough rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've been apologizing and\Nsmiling like that the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaori. Why did you come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I'm dragging you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dragging me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, what do you think about Shea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning,\Nwe really treated her roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only see Yue as someone special.\NI hoped Shea would just give up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Shea... She cried,\Nlaughed, and got angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but always seemed to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't use magic,\Nshe got easily overpowered,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she always held her head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never surrendered\Nto her feelings of inferiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm not surrendering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice? After coming here,\Nyou've been apologizing nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also smiling differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face me and look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you again. I love Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone else became important\Nto me, Yue will always be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If hearing that only gives you pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if all you can get from comparing\Nyourself to Yue is a sense of defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Kaori, you shouldn't be around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to speak to everyone\Nabout something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Aiko Hatayama.\NI have come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, nice to meet you too.\NWhat do you mean by "come for me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to eat dinner with my students...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are going to the Divine Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you do not call yourself\Na deity for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am impressed that you resisted my Charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry; I will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a useful pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let someone know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, "Someone Important."